com.koloboke.collect.map.hash

Interface HashDoubleDoubleMap

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Container, DoubleDoubleMap, HashContainer, Map<Double,Double>

    public interface HashDoubleDoubleMap
extends DoubleDoubleMap, HashContainer
    An interface for DoubleDoubleMaps, based on hash tables.

    This interface doesn't carry own specific behaviour, just combines it's superinterfaces.

    Looking for a way to instantiate a HashDoubleDoubleMap? See static factory methods in HashDoubleDoubleMaps class.

    See Also:
    HashDoubleDoubleMapFactory, HashDoubleDoubleMaps, @KolobokeMap
